NOTES

This is very incomplete right now. 

INSTALLATION

To run tofuhunt you will need a few things. The following is the list :

python (http://www.python.org)
pygame (http://www.pygame.org)

There are installation instructions for those on the given sites. 

After you have those all you need to you is run tofuhunt.py from the
command line. 

shell>cd dir/where/tofuhunt/is/located/
shell>python tofuhunt.py

Enjoy! 


WINDOWS

You can download python and pygame for windows and just run tofuhunt.py
But there is also a windows executable provided on the tofuhunt download
site.

MAC OS X

You will have to follow the instructions on http://www.pygame.org on 
how to get it working for OS X. Then just run tofuhunt.py 